demos.review: Do not buy this phone. it is used, no head phone, chip charger not original, no iPhone box

I purchased this phone for my son on July 7 and on August 9 the phone conveniently died. It wouldn't charge at all and sits here as a tribute to my stupidity for listening to my teenage son who told me about purchasing a refurbished phone-- I know betterTHIS IS A SCAM! Do not buy this phone!
